DataElement.preferredName: Personal Medical History Performed Observation Outcome End Relative Value Reference Object Temporal Qualifier Code ISO21090.CD.v1.0
DataElement.preferredDefinition: A coded value specifying the end of the medical history event with respect to the sponsor-defined reference period. EXAMPLE(S): before, during, during/after, after. NOTE(S): Sponsors should define the reference period in the study metadata.
